# UI Component Rules

- All visual components should be written in React with JSX.
- Use Tailwind CSS utility classes and daisyUI elements.
- Do not use inline styles or dynamically injected CSS from JavaScript.
- Any third-party UI should be abstracted behind reusable internal components.
